      "span_text": "FA represents the degree of diffusion anisotropy and reflects the degree of alignment of cellular structure.  The diffusion of water within the tissues may be altered by changes in the tissue microstructure due to different pathological processes of the central nervous system, including demyelination, axonal damage, inflammation, oedema and ischaemia."
